title: The Annual AFC Over/Unders With Cousin Sal | The Bill Simmons Podcast
description:
In Part 1 of their two-part podcast, Bill Simmons and Cousin Sal gear up for the 2019 NFL regular season by running through each team in the AFC and talking odds, sleepers, parlays, Parent Corner, and more!
